title: DipTrace v 2.4.0.2
description:
DipTrace is quality Schematic Capture and PCB Design software, which offers everything to create simple or complex multi-layer board from the schematic to the state of ready manufacturing files.

This is the trial version craked to Full Edition.

Install instructions:

1. Install DipTrace with diptrace_en.exe (30 days limited trial).

2. Wait until install finish and replace Schematic.exe and Pcb.exe files in "Program Files (x86)DipTrace".

3. Install 3D models library by running models3d.exe installer.

4. Enjoy the software and if you make profits using the software please support de developpers.
